  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "R3GU1lMPgxMaTX/sEY3iiED8FCY=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# subscription-instance model tracks active customer subscriptions with lifecycle state\n\n`powerhouse/subscription-instance` represents an active customer subscription. It is initialized from a ServiceOffering's final configuration.\n\n## State Shape\n\n```graphql\ntype SubscriptionInstanceState {\n    customerId: PHID               # \u2192 customer identity (external)\n    customerName: String\n    customerEmail: EmailAddress\n    customerType: CustomerType     # INDIVIDUAL | TEAM\n    operatorId: PHID               # \u2192 BuilderProfile (external)\n    serviceOfferingId: PHID        # \u2192 ServiceOffering\n    tierName: String\n    selectedBillingCycle: BillingCycle\n    resource: ResourceDocument     # { id: PHID!, label, thumbnailUrl }\n    status: SubscriptionStatus!    # PENDING | ACTIVE | PAUSED | EXPIRING | CANCELLED\n    services: [Service!]!\n    serviceGroups: [ServiceGroup!]!\n    # ... lifecycle timestamps, billing projections, budget, autoRenew\n}\n```\n\n## Modules (5)\n\n| Module | Operations | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------|\n| subscription | 16 | Initialize, status transitions, customer info, tier info, billing projections, renewal |\n| service | 9 | Add/remove services, setup/recurring costs, facet selections |\n| service-group | 5 | Add/remove groups, add/remove services to groups, group costs |\n| metrics | 5 | Add/update/remove service metrics, increment/decrement usage |\n| customer | 2 | Set customer type, update team member count |\n\n## Key References\n\n- `serviceOfferingId: PHID` \u2192 ServiceOffering (source offering)\n- `operatorId: PHID` \u2192 BuilderProfile (external)\n- `customerId: PHID` \u2192 customer identity (external)\n- `resource.id: PHID` \u2192 ResourceInstance (via ResourceDocument)\n- Services/groups mirror ServiceOffering structure but with billing actuals\n\n## Data Flow\n\nServiceOffering \u2192 (mapOfferingToSubscription) \u2192 SubscriptionInstance initialization. Since [[mapOfferingToSubscription transforms service offering state into subscription initialization]], this is the primary cross-model data flow.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[schema design]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z"
    }
  },
